Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱多了10元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是诚实呢 明明是不良少年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.78,0:05:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:34.33,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点都不诚实的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说他之前侍奉过那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以以前就知道我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.72,0:05:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是那个男人的未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:45.47,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…just because my…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也说被我救过
